strings.Value: "My tooth hurts. I should get it healed... Though what's the point if I'll die soon anyway?"
"If you heal your toothache, most honorable Harrim, you will be able to die without being distracted by trifles! Toothaches can be an awful distraction, even on one's deathbed..."
